<p>
The Editorial Office is responsible for collation, minimal formatting,
and publication of materials currently available to the archive.
</p>

<p>
Where signatures are missing, names are withheld.
Where certainty is unavailable, uncertainty is preserved.
</p>

<p>
Correspondence may be addressed to the Editorial Office.
Responses are not guaranteed.
</p>

